{"tid":901724,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★恐怖！食水現大量肉蟲　居民飲用後嘔吐過敏不適","createTime":"2018-11-14T08:54:19.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-03T07:23:59.000Z","uid":19454,"like":205,"dislike":19,"uniUserReply":80,"replies":[{"pid":"474a43c4f897539f6a6c5301034d47bc70920282","tid":901724,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-14T08:54:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/cnnews/20181113/photo/bkn-20181113115112979-1113_00952_001_01b.jpg?20181113233722\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fcnnews%2F20181113%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20181113115112979-1113_00952_001_01b.jpg%3F20181113233722&h=8f881000&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/cnnews/20181113/photo/bkn-20181113115112979-1113_00952_001_02b.jpg?20181113233722\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fcnnews%2F20181113%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20181113115112979-1113_00952_001_02b.jpg%3F20181113233722&h=d796b928&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n北京市海淀區一屋苑有多名住戶爆料稱，近半個月自來水中驚現大量不明肉蟲。有多人疑因喝下有蟲食水而出現嘔吐、過敏等症狀。目前當地衞生計生部門，及屋苑物業管理處已就事件展開調查。<br />\n<br />\n據報道，自上周二（6日）開始陸續有居民發現，有肉蟲在自來水中游動。目前該屋苑的15座住宅中，有12座共24戶表示，發現家中自來水有肉蟲，令居民的生活陷入儲多不便。居民亦擔心，區內免疫力較低的老人和小孩最受影響。<br />\n<br />\n一名李姓女業主稱，周日（11日）晚上其丈夫在刷牙時，發現水龍頭流出一條長約1厘米的黑色肉蟲。自此，家人連煮好的自來水都不敢再飲用。因不敢用自來水，家人已經有1星期時間沒有梳洗，穿過的衣服也堆積起來。即使能到樓下打水，但因沒有儲水工具，只能用鍋、水盆等，一天更要上落來回好幾趟。<br />\n<br />\n李女及另外兩名分別姓曹、姓董的女業主表示，自己及家人疑因飲用帶蟲自來水，出現各種病痛。李女半歲大的兒子背部大面積起痘﹔曹女的孩子半個月內出現3次腹痛，且有眼下紅腫的過敏症狀；而董女自10月底持續一周發燒及拉肚子，現時還偶然腹痛。<br />\n<br />\n物管處周日貼出通告稱，自來水集團和衞計委已派人抽驗水質，清洗和消毒屋苑的供水設施，並調來兩部水車讓居民取水。及至周一（12日）有居民指出，自來水不僅帶有濃烈的消毒水味，而且水中還能清楚看到些許黑色沉澱物和幾條肉蟲在游動。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/cnnews/20181113/bkn-20181113115112979-1113_00952_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fcnnews%2F20181113%2Fbkn-20181113115112979-1113_00952_001.html&d=wzPql2HN1U%2FdtEo8BWkm%2BZZgE6vMW1KEzMhkvokIvkY%3D&h=f45e2b77\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/cnnews/20181113/bkn-20181113115112979-1113_00952_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"ad67e6c0986693c6fa6734a62a2e43cb63639fed","tid":901724,"uid":19454,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-14T08:54:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b02ffcff4d293faaf5860b666e6cee9bcdd902f","tid":901724,"uid":19454,"like":178,"dislike":1,"score":177,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-14T08:55:12.000Z","msg":"支那屎水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"303d517c3a4189561161f0ad2cef223ebb11d9d7","tid":901724,"uid":19527,"like":110,"dislike":1,"score":109,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-14T08:56:47.000Z","msg":"同類相食<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b05d14a38003121fce2a907a14f7de58415ceef","tid":901724,"uid":10064,"like":25,"dislike":0,"score":25,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-14T08:57:45.000Z","msg":"無毒"},{"pid":"dffefaaea34f5277a1e471d0149b4e4a6cb84f08","tid":901724,"uid":137921,"like":133,"dislike":1,"score":132,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-14T08:59:51.000Z","msg":"含有豐富蛋白質 支那人居然不懂欣賞黨的心意"},{"pid":"b4bed5574c45bab008141d2965b2a9f5139c3a97","tid":901724,"uid":19454,"like":443,"dislike":2,"score":441,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-14T09:02:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://2.bp.blogspot.com/-HcGD-gYZVAc/WONjXul_BRI/AAAAAAABdXU/aeYz3T5yuSsvt3U-gqxO0hAC0OPV-1qogCLcB/s640/IMG_1904.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F2.bp.blogspot.com%2F-HcGD-gYZVAc%2FWONjXul_BRI%2FAAAAAAABdXU%2FaeYz3T5yuSsvt3U-gqxO0hAC0OPV-1qogCLcB%2Fs640%2FIMG_1904.JPG&h=7640ea6c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4c72512dcd1b3602ce2e2efb95e735f3f2dae794","tid":901724,"uid":11719,"like":302,"dislike":1,"score":301,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-14T09:04:17.000Z","ms