":8,"score":-8,"quote":{"pid":"474a43c4f897539f6a6c5301034d47bc70920282","tid":901724,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-14T08:54:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/cnnews/20181113/photo/bkn-20181113115112979-1113_00952_001_01b.jpg?20181113233722\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fcnnews%2F20181113%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20181113115112979-1113_00952_001_01b.jpg%3F20181113233722&h=8f881000&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/cnnews/20181113/photo/bkn-20181113115112979-1113_00952_001_02b.jpg?20181113233722\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fcnnews%2F20181113%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20181113115112979-1113_00952_001_02b.jpg%3F20181113233722&h=d796b928&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n北京市海淀區一屋苑有多名住戶爆料稱，近半個月自來水中驚現大量不明肉蟲。有多人疑因喝下有蟲食水而出現嘔吐、過敏等症狀。目前當地衞生計生部門，及屋苑物業管理處已就事件展開調查。<br />\n<br />\n據報道，自上周二（6日）開始陸續有居民發現，有肉蟲在自來水中游動。目前該屋苑的15座住宅中，有12座共24戶表示，發現家中自來水有肉蟲，令居民的生活陷入儲多不便。居民亦擔心，區內免疫力較低的老人和小孩最受影響。<br />\n<br />\n一名李姓女業主稱，周日（11日）晚上其丈夫在刷牙時，發現水龍頭流出一條長約1厘米的黑色肉蟲。自此，家人連煮好的自來水都不敢再飲用。因不敢用自來水，家人已經有1星期時間沒有梳洗，穿過的衣服也堆積起來。即使能到樓下打水，但因沒有儲水工具，只能用鍋、水盆等，一天更要上落來回好幾趟。<br />\n<br />\n李女及另外兩名分別姓曹、姓董的女業主表示，自己及家人疑因飲用帶蟲自來水，出現各種病痛。李女半歲大的兒子背部大面積起痘﹔曹女的孩子半個月內出現3次腹痛，且有眼下紅腫的過敏症狀；而董女自10月底持續一周發燒及拉肚子，現時還偶然腹痛。<br />\n<br />\n物管處周日貼出通告稱，自來水集團和衞計委已派人抽驗水質，清洗和消毒屋苑的供水設施，並調來兩部水車讓居民取水。及至周一（12日）有居民指出，自來水不僅帶有濃烈的消毒水味，而且水中還能清楚看到些許黑色沉澱物和幾條肉蟲在游動。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/cnnews/20181113/bkn-20181113115112979-1113_00952_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fcnnews%2F20181113%2Fbkn-20181113115112979-1113_00952_001.html&d=wzPql2HN1U%2FdtEo8BWkm%2BZZgE6vMW1KEzMhkvokIvkY%3D&h=f45e2b77\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/cnnews/20181113/bkn-20181113115112979-1113_00952_001.html</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-14T10:13:18.000Z","msg":"痴撚線，飲左個d成身寄生蟲，快d照照佢喇"},{"pid":"0e8b1dd7632a65ba292a5e62f848eb37cbaa3e37","tid":901724,"uid":121546,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-14T10:17:50.000Z","msg":"係被激敗既80年後,中央政府終於效法大和民族改善國民既膳食營養<br />\n一日一杯水,振興一個民族<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa5b80dc7a1c11e54ba854b3477c86c8bf68883b","tid":901724,"uid":121546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-14T10:18:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>係被擊敗既80年後,中央政府終於效法大和民族改善國民既膳食營養<br />\n一日一杯水,振興一個民族<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"8a925647832bf3c429c2d755a5ed02333d29a125","tid":901724,"uid":4525,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-14T10:27:40.000Z","msg":"蛋白質水<br />\n中國人就好啦"},{"pid":"c426a3f43dbd2d3398955b495ddf690512335bf1","tid":901724,"uid":173271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-14T10:29:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a4c39302f4d257b71de9f9d0c3e188bf0c3c7b79","tid":901724,"uid":34571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-14T10:30:34.000Z","msg":"血變<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"901f12d3fe2407c68dd0851659d729b499679622","tid":901724,"uid":10637,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-14T10:31:30.000Z","msg":"發生係美國tvb一定會報<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9553e639f4de8fa9a1ec8acb4940e8eed7482dbb","tid":901724,"uid":94662,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-14T10:32:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d5b070fc20884e35078565561538203b869589d","tid":901724,"uid":219194,